      227.77,
      526.21,
      282.48
    ],
    "text": "Investigations have been initiated based on information received by the Panamura Police Station on the night of 05.04.2026, regarding an incident in which a person was attacked with sharp weapons in the Weathura area of the Panamura Police Division and subsequently succumbed to injuries after being admitted to Panamura Hospital.",
    "fonts": [
