    "bbox": [
      107.42,
      170.58,
      340.06,
      185.59
    ],
    "text": "Suspicious death \u2013 Galle Police Division",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPS-BoldMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      13.5600004196167
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      107.42,
      200.05,
      526.41,
      254.76
    ],
    "text": "Investigations have been initiated by the Galle Police Station following a complaint received on the evening of 05.04.2026 regarding the death of a person under suspicious circumstances at a residence in the Weliwatte area of the Galle Police Division.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      107.42,
      269.2,
      403.75,
      282.48
    ],
    "text": "The deceased is a 48-year-old resident of the Weliwatte area.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      107.42,
      297.04,
      526.19,
      337.92
    ],
    "text": "It has been reported that the deceased returned home intoxicated on the night of 04.04.2026 and went to sleep with a head injury. It was later discovered that he had died during the night, as he did not wake up the following day.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      107.42,
      352.48,
      526.4,
      379.56
    ],
    "text": "The body has been placed at the Karapitiya Hospital mortuary for post-mortem examination. Further investigations are being carried out by the Galle Police.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
